body:
# Cozy Jozy
Track and Analyze your child's Diapers, Feedings and more!

***

## Features
* Track Feedings (Bottle / Nursing, Duration and Amount)
* Track Diaper Changes 
* Track Sleep
* Visual Analytics
* Track multiple children
* Grant access to other users to edit or view
* Free
